In reviewing a project, the committee shall determine whether the project has met all the relevant requirements of:
KRS 45.750 to 45.816;
KRS 56.800 to 56.823; and
Any other statutes relating to the committee's oversight of:
Capital projects;
The allotment and expenditure of funds from the emergency repair, maintenance, and replacement account and the capital construction and equipment purchase contingency account;
The state's acquisition of capital assets, including the lease of real property;
The issuance of bonds by the Commonwealth, and the related individual projects; and
Bonds issued by or on behalf of local school districts.
